Ivan Rakitic of Sevilla Football Club recently spotted wearing the all new @geraldcharles_official Maestro GC 3.0 Chronograph in stainless steel with black dial. 
Inspired by the architecture of Francesco Borromini for the Maestro’s case, it is powered by an ultra-thin movement made by the masters watchmakers of Vaucher Manufacture in Fleurier and features a chronograph without date with three counters for seconds, minutes and hours.
